==Swedish==
{{wikipedia}}
===Etymology===
Compound of ''[[fil]]'' (originally meaning [[cream]]) and ''[[mjölk]]'' ([[milk]])
===Noun===
'''filmjölk'''

# a kind of fermented and soured [[milk]]

====Usage note====
*It is common to abbreviate the word to simply ''[[fil]]'', but this can also denote a larger family of similar soured milk products. 

